#. module: coal_petroleum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coal_petroleum.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">Allowed Quantity</font></"
"strong>: The Allowed quantity is determined through an automated action "
"called \"Allowed Quantity on Transfer.\" This action calculates the quantity "
"by\n"
"               subtracting the tolerance percentage from the demand quantity "
"of the receipt transfer. (Studio)"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">Cantidad permitida</font></"
"strong>: La cantidad permitida se determina a través de una acción "
"automatizada llamada “Cantidad de traslado permitido” que calcula la "
"cantidad\n"
"                restando el porcentaje de tolerancia a la cantidad "
"solicitada del traslado de recepción. (Studio)"

#. module: coal_petroleum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coal_petroleum.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">Quality Parameters</font></"
"strong>: The field was created in accordance with the standards and "
"requirements of the coal industry, encompassing a range of tests and\n"
"               parameters. (Studio)"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">Parámetros de calidad</"
"font></strong>: Este campo se creó de acuerdo con las normas y requisitos "
"del sector del carbón, que engloba varias pruebas y\n"
"               parámetros. (Studio)"

#. module: coal_petroleum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coal_petroleum.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">Tolerance</font></strong>: "
"Tolerance is a field that has been created on the purchase form, allowing us "
"to define a tolerance percentage. refers to minimizing the environmental\n"
"               impact associated with the transportation of coal from mines "
"to end-users. (Studio)"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">Tolerancia</font></strong>: "
"El campo “Tolerancia” se encuentra en el formulario de compra y permite "
"definir un porcentaje de tolerancia. Se refiere a minimizar el impacto "
"ambiental \n"
"                asociado a la transportación del carbón desde las minas "
"hasta los usuarios finales. (Studio)"

#. module: coal_petroleum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coal_petroleum.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">Vehicle Number</font>: </"
"strong>It is required to provide the vehicle number for the purpose of "
"formal documentation. Please ensure that the vehicle number associated with "
"the\n"
"               selected transportation mode, whether it is a Truck, Ship, or "
"Train, is accurately provided. (Studio)"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">Número de vehículo</font>: "
"</strong> Es necesario que proporcione el número de vehículo para la "
"documentación correspondiente, asegúrese de que el número de vehículo "
"asociado con el \n"
"               modo de transporte seleccionado, ya sea camión, barco o tren, "
"sea correcto. (Studio)"

#. module: coal_petroleum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coal_petroleum.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);\">tolerance</font><font "
"style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"> </font></strong>percentage line-wise "
"(Studio) 5%"
msgstr ""
"Añada el porcentaje de <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 0);"
"\">tolerancia</font><font style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"> </font></"
"strong>a cada línea (Studio): 5 %."

